snippet.title: Sonic Sundown CGS Promo
snippet.description:
You can play the SHC version of the demo right now: https://shc.zone/entries/contest2024/1111 (where it won 6 trophies!)
A Chao Games Showcase version of the same demo is also coming soon with a few fixes here and there! Stay tuned for that!

Massive thanks to FlapperUltra for the trailer and MDTravis for the VHS capture!
Music: Astrophysics
